@blkslymn Where did I ever say that? Majority of my portfolio is concentrated in photonics with names like $SIVE and $AAOI.

However, I’m allowed to talk about other exciting developments as well… Such as the first listed US humanoid player?

I still think CPO/optics has the fastest TAM

